OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FUTV can reveal that the vast majority
OL,6,Fof a #230million funding pot given to
OL,7,FStormont two years ago to transform
OL,8,Fpublic services has not yet been spent.
OL,10,FStormont departments have confirmed
OL,11,Fjust #9m of the fund given to the
OL,12,FExecutive by the former Prime Minister
OL,13,FRishi Sunak as part of the package for
OL,14,FStormont's return in 2024 has been
OL,15,Fused so far.
OL,17,FThat is just under 4% of the total
OL,18,Ffund and leading to questions as to
OL,19,Fhow the Executive can say it has no
OL,20,Fmoney.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
