OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe funds are specifically earmarked
OL,6,Ffor making public services more
OL,7,Fefficient.
OL,9,FLast March the Finance Minister John
OL,10,FO'Dowd announced that four Stormont
OL,11,Fdepartments would receive a share of
OL,12,Fthe first tranche of the funding -
OL,13,F#129m.
OL,15,FThe Department of Health was given
OL,16,F#61m to make services more accessible
OL,17,Fin communities through
OL,18,FMultidisciplinary Teams. It has
OL,19,Fconfirmed to UTV that #7m of the
OL,20,Ffunding has been used so far.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe Department of Justice was
OL,6,Fallocated #22m for two projects to
OL,7,Fspeed up justice and to update
OL,8,Felectronic tagging. The department
OL,9,Fsays #258,000 has been spent.
OL,11,FThe Department for Infrastructure has
OL,12,Fa total of #18m to improve drainage
OL,13,Fand planning. It has spent #375,000.
OL,15,FWhile the Department of Education was
OL,16,Fgiven #27.5m for its project aimed at
OL,17,Ftransforming Special Education. It has
OL,18,Fspent just #1m.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
