OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FIn recent weeks the Education Minister
OL,6,FPaul Givan has told the Assembly he
OL,7,Fneeds more money to transform SEN
OL,8,Fprovision.
OL,10,FThrough a freedom of information
OL,11,Frequest UTV has also seen the minutes
OL,12,Fof meetings of the Transformation
OL,13,FBoard tasked with overseeing the
OL,14,Ffunding. It is chaired by the Head of
OL,15,Fthe Civil Service Jayne Brady.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe minutes show that over the last
OL,6,Fyear members have expressed
OL,7,F'considerable concern' about the level
OL,8,Fof progress across all the projects
OL,9,Fand the 'minimal spend' by the
OL,10,Fdepartments. The board has also asked
OL,11,Ffor assurances that the delay in
OL,12,Fspending the money was not putting the
OL,13,Fprojects at risk.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
