CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe Transformation Board minutes
OL,6,Fdetail how members have had particular
OL,7,Fconcerns around the 'size and scale'
OL,8,Fof the Education Department's project
OL,9,Fto transform Special Educational
OL,10,FNeeds. Officials have repeatedly
OL,11,Fexpressed caution around the plans and
OL,12,Fhave sought assurances that it will
OL,13,Fdeliver what it intends.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe SDLP Leader of the Opposition at
OL,6,FStormont Matthew O'Toole has said:
OL,7,F"Clearly it takes time to deliver
OL,8,Flarge scale transformation, but you
OL,9,Fcan't on the one hand complain about
OL,10,Flack of money and tell the public that
OL,11,Fyou have no money to help them with
OL,12,Ffor example the cost of living, while
OL,13,Fat the same time you are literally
OL,14,Fleaving tens if not hundreds of
OL,15,Fmillions of pounds of transformation
OL,16,Fmoney simply unspent."
OL,18,FThe departments maintain they are
OL,19,Fmaking progress with their projects.
OL,26,@xD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
