OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FThe Executive Office said:
OL,6,F"Transforming public services is an
OL,7,FExecutive priority, with the
OL,8,FTransformation Fund deliberately
OL,9,Fdesigned to support sustained,
OL,10,Fsystemlevel change. The Fund operates
OL,11,Fas a fouryear programme, recognising
OL,12,Fthat meaningful reform requires phased
OL,13,Fdelivery."
OL,15,FDuring a press conference last week
OL,16,Fthe first minister admitted
OL,17,Ftransformation was not easy to deliver
OL,18,Fquickly.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,FMichelle O'Neill said: "They take time
OL,6,Fto make a difference, you don't just
OL,7,Fdecide you are going to turn off
OL,8,Fsomething and turn something else on
OL,9,Fand you get an immediate result,
OL,10,Funfortunately, I wish that was the
OL,11,Freality but it's not."
OL,13,FThe Finance Minister John O'Dowd
OL,14,Fdefended the roll out of the money.
OL,26,@mD@XOUsD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
