PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1776885106
OL,3,CRevealed: Stormont's unspent millions
OL,5,F"It will take time for that investment
OL,6,Fto filter through. The board's job is
OL,7,Fmonitor and scrutinise the spend and
OL,8,FI'm content at this stage we are
OL,9,Fmaking progress, I as Minister will
OL,10,Fcontinue to monitor that situation
OL,11,Fmyself," he told UTV's View From
OL,12,FStormont.
OL,14,F"But it has to be minded this
OL,15,Fprogramme only started last year, the
OL,16,Finvestment is in place. It will take
OL,17,Ftime for it to step up and ramp up,
OL,18,Fbut I will continue to monitor the
OL,19,Fsituation along with the board."
OL,26,@mD@AOUvD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
